CREATE TABLE "api_resena" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "calificacion" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("calificacion" >= 0), "comentario" text NOT NULL, "respuesta_prestador" text NULL, "fecha_creacion" datetime NOT NULL, "aprobada" bool NOT NULL, "object_id" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("object_id" >= 0), "content_type_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "usuario_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "api_customuser" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED); (params None)
CREATE TABLE "api_resena" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "calificacion" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("calificacion" >= 0), "comentario" text NOT NULL, "respuesta_prestador" text NULL, "fecha_creacion" datetime NOT NULL, "aprobada" bool NOT NULL, "object_id" integer unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("object_id" >= 0), "content_type_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "usuario_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "api_customuser" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED); (params None)
CREATE TABLE "api_respuestausuario" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "respuesta" text NOT NULL CHECK ((JSON_VALID("respuesta") OR "respuesta" IS NULL)), "fecha_respuesta" datetime NOT NULL, "pregunta_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "api_pregunta" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "usuario_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "api_customuser" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED); (params None)
CREATE TABLE "api_respuestausuario" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "respuesta" text NOT NULL CHECK ((JSON_VALID("respuesta") OR "respuesta" IS NULL)), "fecha_respuesta" datetime NOT NULL, "pregunta_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "api_pregunta" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "usuario_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "api_customuser" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED); (params None)
